<h1 id="n×n-矩阵计算" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#n×n-矩阵计算" aria-hidden="true">#</a> n×n 矩阵计算</h1>
<h2 id="n×n-矩阵" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#n×n-矩阵" aria-hidden="true">#</a> n×n 矩阵</h2>
<p>若<code v-pre>A = (a[i][j])</code>和<code v-pre>B = (b[i][j])</code>为 n × n 的方阵，则对<code v-pre>i, j = 1, 2, ..., n</code>，定义乘积<code v-pre>C = A · B</code>中的元素<code v-pre>c[i][j]</code>为：</p>
<p><img src="https://github-imglib-1255459943.cos.ap-chengdu.myqcloud.com/1487758346(1).png" alt="image"></p>
